<p>The funds will enable her to spend eight weeks conducting research in Singapore this summer. </p>
<p>Richardson's research interests are in fieldwork and usability testing, specifically she is interested in the transition technology makes from the research setting into natural/real life settings. She is  also interested in technologies to facilitate learning and communication across cultures. </p>
